"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"## My search for an acre of escape\\n\\n[![Paul Greenberg](https://miro.medium.com/fit/c/56/56/1\\\\*tPfbBeQ23qMKUptWlw1FaQ.jpeg)](https://4fishgreenberg.medium.com/?source=post_page-----82252fbaae82-----------------------------------)\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*lvzvn8HdxUe8BXEsPxlZ5w.png)\\n\\n“Granite erratic, Dudmaston” by Richard Webb is licensed under CC BY-SA 2.0. To view a copy of this license, visit <https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.0/?ref=openverse&atype=rich>\\n\\nIt was the rock that caught my eye. Dappled with lichen and lighted by the afternoon sun, it appeared to be the perfect place for contemplation. A spot where you could sit and write your novel, ponder your place in the universe, and perhaps reach some kind of equilibrium with the planet.\\n\",\"timestamp\":1640328155,\"title\":\"Is Anywhere Safe from Climate Change? - Paul Greenberg - Medium\"},\"digest\":\"PzNq7hIIUhlg-d-O2EKVhUkc-HLMDzX5INKetDoF_u4\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xa04A0a0938861cEaf267eb67DE81Bd755d76a12f\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"5WmHHWjx-8E5Fm3kdajVWpD5K8mHkfB9ixjuoFD4OLE\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"VhVfU2_scizvzHlJMYHcoSNKWSFdd0KqA6OpvcZf_GI\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"ZHWButTpqaMn1NEeFopqYhUnzth7BCqnc36u6KqB-ww3pG33BeY3sr55yOpLBGW2kPr0BlqylXQ8RKohGPZJjw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x7e3d4f2cbd4a648e9d19f380efa1ac01b674f3e6b5c2c52aa4025eeb782e16a901539cf88c06490c398968fa69fc99a1700685b63703642df97e980abe3a434a1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"5WmHHWjx-8E5Fm3kdajVWpD5K8mHkfB9ixjuoFD4OLE\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"VhVfU2_scizvzHlJMYHcoSNKWSFdd0KqA6OpvcZf_GI\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"origi